Class RowManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.contentmine.svg2xml.table.RowManager

  • public class RowManager
extends java.lang.Object
    manages the addition and sorting of the row-like objects in a table. these include: - long and short horizontalRules - sibling rules - phraseLists with common Y - contentBox panels
